{"tid":414744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天眼直擊】密斗旺角連掃路邊13車 驚險一刻曝光","createTime":"2017-09-26T12:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T00:03:04.000Z","uid":34252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"82abbd7604700df0c75e6e2734035c2dbb8b44d9","tid":414744,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"下午2時半許，一輛輕型貨車由旺角砵蘭街轉入基隆街時，突然失控衝前約150米，橫跨柏樹街，連環撞毀13輛停泊在路邊的車輛始停下，其中一部車冒煙，消防接報到場拖喉戒備。事件中一名女途人受輕傷，須由救護車送院治理，警方正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n肇事貨車的跟車工人王先生表示，司機叫阿文，負責運送泰國食品，事發時由砵蘭街轉入基隆時已撞及路邊兩部車，他形容當時「好驚」，連忙提醒阿文，惟阿文仍若無其事繼續行駛，沿途再撞十多部車輛始停下。王先生又稱，事發後，阿文神情呆滯，似仍不知道發生車禍。<br />\n其中一名苦主黃先生指，事發時聽到貨櫃車當時將車停於路邊，然後走入一間餐廳用膳，詎料突然聽到一聲「嘭」巨響，黃形容「好似打雷咁」，他立即走出餐廳查看，驚見一部密斗車將十多部車輛掃毀，面目全非。黃狠批肇事司機離譜，「正常撞到第一架都識停」，並慨嘆遭受無妄之災。<br />\n附近商店的閉路電視拍下事發時的驚險一刻，據片段所見，貨車首先撞到路旁另一部貨車，但未有停下，繼續向前連環掃毀多部停泊路邊的車輛，將其推上行人路，路人見狀大驚，紛紛走避。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[實拍] 深水埗基隆街有貨車連撞13架車 街車扁成咁樣樣?!</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ok21y6uhOSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fok21y6uhOSw&d=Ct65v9LZ6WpC%2F1HjwhsYJJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6054b01a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ok21y6uhOSw</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[實拍] 深水埗基隆街貨車連撞13街車後白煙密佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YbAWTNF-rlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYbAWTNF-rlE&d=Ct65v9LZ6WpC%2F1HjwhsYJJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=91c82871\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YbAWTNF-rlE</a>"},{"pid":"c68d047d89c132442d152990cac498d821eebf2c","tid":414744,"uid":40801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望啲死人冧樓好停喇。"},{"pid":"2af90e56181528e4c792d4a76f05f05b0d1c2b26","tid":414744,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"咁多架車, 佢個保險都claim到爆啦, 今次車主要食自己多"},{"pid":"c898dbd53a3eaf96c73ca1a6d631362af74b60f5","tid":414744,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多架車, 佢個保險都claim到爆啦, 今次車主要食自己多</blockquote><br />\n無人死傷都claim爆，到死人咪唔駛有得賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a7f2a6fcc2683565bc3b99f3237aa5fb1ab548","tid":414744,"uid":44462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"天眼係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de28ed082bf64538511417427b25ec511f1a4778","tid":414744,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e86324c59cf3684901fb0d0948311fe24bd9e6b","tid":414744,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"貨車司機賠到破產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a632e3d552b73012edcbb432cc7c7e2cea0264de","tid":414744,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:52:08.000Z","msg":"gta"},{"pid":"25ab43941e3ca0c68878c3422b3c8fb323059084","tid":414744,"uid":14244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"又係深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c6ee813f19e0a6b9b8d04bb2c9f9c5b0aa2baa","tid":414744,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"驚險一刻呢？"},{"pid":"6f73ab6ff9df40f76d25b98e8da0c95bfcca1de1","tid":414744,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚險一刻呢？</blockquote><br />\n睇嚟過度曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48066455e49ca74510e7cd544d84e64365f7ccc","tid":414744,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":